### [Numbers Chapter 21](../../../bib/kjv/num021.htm#001.md)

[Numbers 21:3](../../../bib/kjv/num021.htm#003.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_003">num 21:3</span></span>

Hormah

That is, utter destruction.

[Numbers 21:9](../../../bib/kjv/num021.htm#009.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_009">num 21:9</span></span>

serpent

(See Scofield) - ([Gen 3:14](../../../bib/kjv/gen003.htm#014).md).

The serpent is a symbol of sin judged; brass speaks of the divine
judgment, as in the brazen altar

(See Scofield) - ([Exo 27:1](../../../bib/kjv/exo027.htm#001).md)",

note (2) and self-judgment, as in the laver of brass. The brazen serpent
is a type of Christ "made sin for us"; ([Joh
3:14](../../../bib/kjv/joh003.htm#014).md); ([Joh
3:15](../../../bib/kjv/joh003.htm#015).md); ([Co2
5:21](../../../bib/kjv/co2005.htm#021).md) in bearing our judgment.
Historically, the moment is indicated in the cry: "My God, My God, why
hast Thou forsaken Me?" ([Mat 27:46](../../../bib/kjv/mat027.htm#046).md).

[Numbers 21:17](../../../bib/kjv/num021.htm#017.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_017">num 21:17</span></span>

Then Israel

The spiritual order here is beautiful:

\(1\) atonement ([Num 21:8](../../../bib/kjv/num021.htm#008).md); ([Num
21:9](../../../bib/kjv/num021.htm#009).md); ([Joh
3:14](../../../bib/kjv/joh003.htm#014).md); ([Joh
3:15](../../../bib/kjv/joh003.htm#015).md).

\(2\) water, symbol of the Spirit bestowed ([Num
21:16](../../../bib/kjv/num021.htm#016).md); ([Joh
7:37-39](../../../bib/kjv/joh007.htm#037).md).

\(3\) joy ([Num 21:17](../../../bib/kjv/num021.htm#017).md); ([Num
21:18](../../../bib/kjv/num021.htm#018).md); ([Rom
14:17](../../../bib/kjv/rom014.htm#017).md).

\(4\) power ([Num 21:21-24](../../../bib/kjv/num021.htm#021).md).

